codex
The sandbox only lets this turn write inside `execution-framework`, so writing to the package parent’s `migration-artifacts/` is correctly blocked. The registry helper already supports an `execution-framework/migration-artifacts` fallback, so I’m adjusting the generator to place the files in the writable artifact directory while registering them under the packet-relative paths.
apply patch
